data.description: Beautiful single level home with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths! This home sits on an oversized lot with an RV gate, you will be blown away with what this home has to offer! The corner lot provides plenty of space for all your backyard needs with an extended covered patio, amazing grass and so much more. Inside is an open concept kitchen with a breakfast bar/island, gas cooktop, beautiful backsplash, neutral colors, and a walk-in pantry. The family room has a large double glass sliding door and shutters are included on every window! This amazing split floor plan provides privacy for your master bedroom that also includes a walk in closet and oversized shower with dual heads. See photos for what the beautiful Village at Vistancia community has to offer!
